00:00:44.760 --> 00:00:49.350
But California hasn’t been getting the precipitation
it needs for the past 4 years and now they’re

00:00:49.350 --> 00:00:51.380
scrambling for new sources of drinking water.

00:00:51.380 --> 00:00:54.710
Los Angeles county is offering to buy water
